  continueButton: {fileID: 230337558}
  gentleModeToggleButton: {fileID: 0}
  gentleModeToggle: {fileID: 0}
  gentleModeLabel: {fileID: 0}
  defaultBody: 'Welcome to the Hollow.


    This is a quiet game about memory, choice,
    and care.

    There is no combat. There are no failure screens. There are only
    choices.


    Some scenes are heavy. Some are warm. The pace is yours.

    Tools
    at the corner of the screen let you auto-complete any mini-game.

    Gentle
    Mode softens the harder moments. You can toggle it any time.'
